               Operatorlar
// - Bo'lish va butun qismini olish:
5//6 = 0

** - Exponenta(daraja/ildiz):
5**2 = 25

% - bo'linmaning qoldig'ini olish:
15%6 = 3

ildiz ostini topish:
6**(1/2)

\t - matnga bo'shliq qo'shadi:
print("Hello \tWorld!")  - Hello    World!
print("Hello \nWorld!")  - Hello
                           World!


